dataIdInfo.idPurp: Building footprints in the City and County of San Francisco, as of June 2011.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer shows building footprints for the City and County of San Francisco as of June 2011. There were created using the ArcGIS 3D Analyst conversion tool, "MultiPatch Footprint," converting the 3D building model data the City licensed from PIctometry, Inc.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: San Francisco Enterprise GIS Program, Department of Technology Pictometry, Inc.

dataLineage.statement: The initial source of this dataset is the LiDAR data captured in June 2011 by Pictometry, Inc. for the City and County of San Francisco. The LIDAR and the oblique imagery captured in May 2011 by Pictometry were combined to create a 3D building model of the City in various formats, including the .flt format. The .flt format was converted to a 2D polygon feature class representing building footprints in San Francisco, using the ArcGIS 3D Analyst MultiPatch Footprint conversion tool.
